    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 high-performance inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This chassis delivers a raw, analog experience through its Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate known floor-pan stress fractures. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, providing precise turn-in and predictable mid-corner rotation. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the powertrain remains robust, pulling cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. This is a driver-spec example optimized for mechanical longevity and tactile feedback.",
