      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? I'm parting with my car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs smoothly, and has been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this beauty is ready to go! I've taken great care of it and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
